name: Diamond-Hand Otter
description:
Otter royalty sitting on an otterly gorgeous throne. Created by OtterClam’s in-house artist and designer, Apppo.  
  
The rarest NFT in The Otter Kingdom, the Diamond-Hand Otter’s determination is unbreakable and unshakeable. You’ll never get the CLAMs out of this Otter’s diamond hands, but you can always try.
